@startuml
title Klickertool - Struktur mit getrennten Data Sources

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class KlickerConfig <<dataclass>> {
  +output_path: str
  +group_column: str
  +display_columns: list[str]
  +status_column: str = "Status"
  +done_value: str = "done"
  +window_title: str = "Manual Data Selector"
}

class ExcelSourceConfig <<dataclass>> {
  +input_path: str
  +sheet_candidates: tuple[str, ...] = ("Daten", "Sheet1")
}

class DataFrameSourceConfig <<dataclass>> {
  +dataframe: DataFrame
  +all_sheets: dict[str, DataFrame] | None = None
}

interface DataSource {
  +load_main_dataframe(): DataFrame
  +load_all_sheets(): dict[str, DataFrame]
  +save_state(all_sheets: dict[str, DataFrame]): None
}

class ExcelDataSource {
  -config: ExcelSourceConfig
  -logger
  -selected_sheet_name: str
  +load_main_dataframe(): DataFrame
  +load_all_sheets(): dict[str, DataFrame]
  +save_state(all_sheets: dict[str, DataFrame]): None
  -find_sheet_name(): str
}

class DataFrameSource {
  -config: DataFrameSourceConfig
  -logger
  +load_main_dataframe(): DataFrame
  +load_all_sheets(): dict[str, DataFrame]
  +save_state(all_sheets: dict[str, DataFrame]): None
}

class SelectionRepository {
  -config: KlickerConfig
  -source: DataSource
  -data: DataFrame
  -all_sheets: dict[str, DataFrame]
  -logger
  +get_next_group(): tuple[object, DataFrame]
  +save_selected_row(group_key, row_idx): None
  +mark_group_as_done(group_key): None
  +save_state(): None
  +is_processed(): bool
  -validate_required_columns(): None
  -build_groups(): DataFrameGroupBy
}

class KlickerResultWriter {
  -config: KlickerConfig
  -logger
  +append_row(row: DataFrame): None
  +write_rows(rows: DataFrame): None
}

class KlickerGUI {
  -repository: SelectionRepository
  -config: KlickerConfig
  -logger
  -root
  -table
  +run(): None
  -display_next_group(): None
  -display_group(group_data: DataFrame): None
  -on_row_select(event): None
  -on_stop(): None
  -on_resume(): None
}

class "run_klickertool()" as RunKlickertool <<function>> {
  +run_klickertool(config: KlickerConfig, source: DataSource, logger=None): None
}

class MainPy <<client>> {
  +main(): None
}

DataSource <|.. ExcelDataSource
DataSource <|.. DataFrameSource

ExcelDataSource --> ExcelSourceConfig
DataFrameSource --> DataFrameSourceConfig

SelectionRepository --> KlickerConfig
SelectionRepository --> DataSource
SelectionRepository --> KlickerResultWriter

KlickerResultWriter --> KlickerConfig

KlickerGUI --> SelectionRepository
KlickerGUI --> KlickerConfig

RunKlickertool ..> KlickerConfig
RunKlickertool ..> DataSource
RunKlickertool ..> SelectionRepository
RunKlickertool ..> KlickerGUI

MainPy ..> KlickerConfig
MainPy ..> ExcelSourceConfig
MainPy ..> DataFrameSourceConfig
MainPy ..> ExcelDataSource
MainPy ..> DataFrameSource
MainPy ..> RunKlickertool

note right of KlickerConfig
  Enthält nur Anzeige-, Auswahl-
  und Ergebnisparameter.
  Keine Information über die Datenquelle.
end note

note right of SelectionRepository
  Validiert vor groupby:
  - group_column existiert
  - status_column existiert
  - group_column enthält gruppierbare Werte
end note

note bottom of DataSource
  Quelle ist austauschbar:
  Excel-Datei oder bereits erzeugter DataFrame
  aus main.py.
end note

@enduml